<title>ECTC Help Desk Status Reports</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF">

<h2 align=center>ECTC Help Desk Status Reports</h2>
<p>
<h3>January 1996</h3>

    Nanci Brasket is currently the sole member of the Artemis Help Desk,
manning the Artemis Comm & Info Center.  Several discussions took place
during the month about putting in place an automated help desk environment
to handle an increased volume of questions in the future.  Those design
ideas were put on the <a href="taskinfo.html#helpdesk">ASI web site</a>,
but we are still looking for volunteers to research this area further.

<h3>February 1996</h3>

    Nanci Brasket answered numerous questions directed to the Comm and Info
Center.

<h3>March 1996</h3>

    Nanci Brasket answered numerous questions directed to the Comm and Info
Center.  Nanci also added five new images to the ASI image library and
edited a large number of new ADB web pages.

<h3>April 1996</h3>

    Nanci Brasket continued answering questions directed to the Comm and
Info Center.  Nanci also added eight new images to the ASI image library
and edited several hundred ASI web pages.

<h3>May 1996</h3>

    Nanci Brasket continued answering questions directed to the Comm and
Info Center.  Nanci also added thirty-nine new images to the ASI image
library and edited thirty-four new or updated ASI web pages.

<h3>June 1996</h3>

    Nanci Brasket continued answering questions directed to the Comm and
Info Center.  Nanci reorganized the Image Library index into separate
index files for each year.  She also added seventeen new images to the
image library and edited sixty-one new or updated ASI web pages.

<p>
<!-- Nav Bar -->

