<hr size=5>
<H3><center>Joining the Office of Space Flight</center></H3>

The Office of Space Flight (OSF) Technical Committees will always 
welcome new members. If you would like to join an OSF Technical Team,
please fill in the form below. You may join as many as you like. If you
are using a browser that doesn't support forms, send mail to <a
href="mailto:artemis@asi.org"> artemis@asi.org</a> or to
<a href="mailto:osf-admin@asi.org"> osf-admin@asi.org</a>.

