<option> 2) Decent Stage
<option> 3) Lunar Habitat
<option> 4) Ascent Stage
<option> 5) Robotic Element
<option> 6) Ground Support Element
<option> 7) SSTO Concept Design
<option> 8) Lunar Sample Return
</select></td></tr>
