</TD><TD ALIGN="center" COLSTART="2"> <B><A
HREF="http://www.asi.org/asi_index.html">Artemis Society</A></B>
</TD><TD ALIGN="center" COLSTART="3"> <B><A
HREF="http://www.asi.org/adb/index.html">Artemis Data Book</A></B>
</TD><TD ALIGN="center" COLSTART="4"> <B><A HREF="/adb/j/index.html">FAQ</A></B>
</TD><TD ALIGN="center" COLSTART="5"> <B><A HREF="/adb/04/index.html">Reference
Mission</A></B>
