http://asi.virtual.io.com:80/adb/03/03/investment.html 206.224.88.80 19970112203828 text/html 9972
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sun, 12 Jan 1997 20:38:12 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1 IOWeb/1.22
