<DOCHDR>
http://asi.virtual.io.com:80/adb/05/05/03/funding-options.html 206.224.88.80 19970112205558 text/html 13172
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sun, 12 Jan 1997 20:56:02 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1 IOWeb/1.22
Content-type: text/html
Set-Cookie: Apache=widener28710853102562211; expires=Friday, 31-Dec-99 23:59:59 GMT; path=/
