<!-- v 1.0 -->
<h2 align="center">Artemis Data Book</H2>
<h2 align="center">5.5.3.2.5 Lunar Sample Return Goals</H2>
<h2 align="center">Lunar Sample Return Goals</H2>
<P ALIGN=CENTER><I>Simon Rowland</I></P>
<P><HR><P>

<P>The goals of the Lunar Sample Return Mission are:</P>

<ul type=square>
<li>Land a probe on the moon and return a quantity of moon rock to Earth
<li>Generate revenues for investors, a manned lunar exploration base, and
for reinvestment in further probe missions
<li>Gain credibility for private planetary space ventures, the Artemis
Project in particular
<li>Gain hands-on experience for the Artemis Project team
<li>Establish space support infrastructure for moonbase
<li>Bootstrap private enterprise into commercial planetary space
</ul>

<!-- Nav Bar -->
