<DOCHDR>
http://asi.virtual.io.com:80/adb/06/07/organizing-teams.html 206.224.88.80 19970112210857 text/html 14312
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sun, 12 Jan 1997 21:09:01 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1 IOWeb/1.22
Content-type: text/html
Set-Cookie: Apache=widener28710853103341477; expires=Friday, 31-Dec-99 23:59:59 GMT; path=/
