http://asi.virtual.io.com:80/adb/06/07/02/01/01/adv-planning-tc-task.html 206.224.88.80 19970112211041 text/html 6174
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sun, 12 Jan 1997 21:10:45 GMT
