http://asi.virtual.io.com:80/adb/06/07/02/01/01/econ-model-dev-inst.html 206.224.88.80 19970112211159 text/html 6803
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sun, 12 Jan 1997 21:11:42 GMT
