<H3>Joining the Propulsion TC</H3>

<P>The Spacecraft Propulsion Technical Committee always welcomes new
members, reps, or observers. If you would like to join the Propulsion TC,
please fill in the form below and join the team! If you are using a
browser that doesn't support forms, send mail with the type of member you
would like to be to Charles Collier
<a href="mailto:cpcollie@seas.gwu.edu">
&lt;cpcollie@seas.gwu.edu&gt;</a>.</P>

