http://asi.virtual.io.com:80/adb/09/04/01/web-page-forms.html 206.224.88.80 19970112213505 text/html 10128
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sun, 12 Jan 1997 21:35:06 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1 IOWeb/1.22
