</LI>
</UL>
<P><b>*Note*</b><br>
The pages linked below as sources for each program were chosen on the
basis of long-time presence on the Web... However, as you know,  pages can come
and go at any time. If the link does not work, any of  these software packages
can be found using a keyword search on any  major Web search engine such as
Yahoo, Lycos, etc.
<P> A couple of other fine sources are...<BR>
<A HREF="http://mars.superlink.net/dreamwvr/irchome.htm">The Ultimate IRC Home
Page </A><BR>
<A HREF="http://benso.com/">Jim Benson Freesoft IRC Help Page </A>
