<H2 ALIGN=CENTER>Artemis Data Book</H2>

<H2 ALIGN=CENTER>9.8. Real-time Meetings</H2>

<H2 ALIGN=CENTER>Schedule of Regular IRC Meetings</H2>

<CENTER><P>Brian Cesar</P></CENTER>

<P>
<HR></P>

<CENTER><DT>Regularly Scheduled meetings on the SuperLink IRC server
at <B>irc.superlink.net port 6667</B> are as follows:</DT></CENTER>

<DT>&nbsp;</DT>

<CENTER><TABLE BORDER=1 WIDTH="80%" >
<TR>
<TD>Channel Name</TD>

<TD>Time</TD>

<TD>Group</TD>

<TD>Date</TD>
</TR>

<TR>
<TD>#ectc</TD>

<TD>1900 EST</TD>

<TD>ECTC</TD>

<TD>First Sunday of each month</TD>
</TR>
</TABLE></CENTER>

<CENTER><P>This page will be updated as each committee defines their meeting
schedules.  <A HREF="mailto:bcesar@surfsouth.com">Email </A>the maintainer
of this page to add new data.</P></CENTER>

<P><BR>
<!-- Nav Bar --></P>

