<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>M.2.9 Clementine Mission Timeline Summary</TITLE></HEAD><body bgcolor="#FFFFFF"><!-- Artemis Data Book --><!-- ADB section M.2.9 Clementine --><!-- file: /adb/m/02/09/timeline-summary.html --><!-- v 1.0 --><h2 align="center">Artemis Data Book</H2><h2 align="center">M.2.9 Clementine</H2><h2 align="center">Clementine Mission Timeline Summary</H2><P ALIGN=CENTER><I>Marvin Ostrega</I></P><P><HR><P><table cellpadding=2><tr><td> 03/24/92  </td><td> Clementine Design Begins. </td></tr><tr><td> 01/25/94 </td><td> Spacecraft launched at Vandenburg Air ForceBase. </td></tr><tr><td> 02/03/94 </td><td> Departure from low Earth orbit following aneight daycheckout period. </td></tr><tr><td> 02/19/94 </td><td> Following two phasing loop orbits, Clementineinjected intolunar orbit. Lunar orbit, shake down period begins. </td></tr><tr><td> 02/26/94  </td><td> Start of systematic mapping for first cycle.</td></tr><tr><td> 03/26/94 </td><td> First mapping cycle complete, start of secondcycle. </td></tr><tr><td> 04/21/94 </td><td>  Second mapping cycle complete, begin specialobservations. </td></tr><tr><td> 05/05/94  </td><td> Leave Lunar Orbit. </td></tr><tr><td> 05/07/94 </td><td> Clementine satellite suffered on-boardmalfunction thatprevents planned close fly-by of the near-Earth Asteroid Geographos. </td></tr><tr><td> 08/31/94 </td><td> Planned Geographos Fly-by (not accomplished).</td></tr></table><!-- Nav Bar --><hr size="5"><table align=center border=4 cellpadding = 3 cellspacing=2><tr><td align=center> <b><a href="http://www.asi.org/index.html">ArtemisProject</a></b><td align=center> <b><a href="http://www.asi.org/asi_index.html">ArtemisSociety</a></b><td align=center> <b><a href="http://www.asi.org/adb/index.html">ArtemisData Book</a></b><td align=center> <b><a href="/adb/j/index.html">FAQ</a></b><td align=center> <b><a href="/adb/04/index.html">Reference Mission</a></b><td align=center> <b><a href="ht