<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Moon Miners' Manifesto Issue #93</TITLE></HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF"><img src="/Gifs/artlogonb.gif" align=left alt="ASI Logo"><!-- /093/fieldtrip-cartoon.html --><h2 align=center>Mrs. Campbell's 5th Grade History Class Fieldtrip 2059</h2><P><HR WIDTH=80%></P><P><FONT SIZE=2>cartoon by <a href="mailto:OSNXD@wcdc04.pgh.wec.com">Neil Durst</a>, ASI Pittsburgh</P><P><img src="/images/asi199500007.gif" width=576 height=384 alt="Cartoon of 'Mrs. Campbell's 5th grade History class fieldtrip 2059'"></P><font size=2><a href="index.html" target="_top">Back to MMM #93</a></font>&nbsp;<a href="osf.html">&lt;-</a>&nbsp;<a href="space-notes.html">-&gt;</a></BODY></HTML>
