HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sun, 12 Jan 1997 23:38:22 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1 IOWeb/1.22
Content-type: text/html
Set-Cookie: Apache=widener3682853112302158; expires=Friday, 31-Dec-99 23:59:59 GMT; path=/
